Title:Project Coordinator II, Req# 33054800

Location:Culver city,CA (Hybrid)

Contract:6+ Month

Job Description

Assist business development team with regular day to day management of video business.

Such tasks include managing Apple TV channel price increases, eCopy code requests as applicable, help prepare keynote slides, assist with weekly/monthly reporting, miscellaneous video projects, aggregating internal data, light reporting and/or tracking, managing Apple TV channel sunsets across Apple, verifying dates across internal systems, etc.

PayRate: $35-40/hr,W2
